data.description: YOU HAVE TO CHECK OUT THE LOCATION OF THIS HOME ON A MAP, IT IS PRIME FOR FOUNTAIN!!! Plenty of room inside this beautiful ranch style home, 2 car garage, RV Parking, finished basement, solar panels, large back yard and shed. Ranch style Homes in this area are rare to find and go quickly, so jump on this while it's available! Price improved to account for feedback. This is now the best opportunity in the area! Right down the street from Parks, Rec Center, FRRC Arena, Trails, Dog Park, Creek! Close to Dining, Shopping, Grocery, Easy Highway access. Walk to The stadium, Highschool, Early Learning and Elementary School! ***Assumable FHA loan with LOW interest rate (note added 12/26/2023)!***
